Insurance Manager - PT Nissan Financial Services Indonesia
Insurance Manager  -
Insurance Manager
Responsibilities
Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, any field.Required language: EnglishAt least 5 years of working experience in managerial position at Insurance Company or handling Insurance matters at Finance Company.Preferably Manager / Senior Manager.Full-Time position available. Job Description:Review existing insurance package and develop new attractive package.Study the customers need and determine suitable coverage and condition to match with customers’ need. Do benchmarking about insurance package that offered by other finance companies.Provide customer with thorough information and explanation about insurance product as required by OJK.Train, educate as well as provide manual for field people to better understand about insurance knowledge and product.Monitor and follow up customer claim handling as well as handling customers’ complains.Develop close relationship with Nissan After Sales Service / Workshops and Nissan Insurance for continuous service improvement.Regular visit to dealers and workshops.Monitor the effectiveness of giving free maintenance coupon to customers.Study after sales and warranty system for new insurance opportunityUpdate with current and updated OJK regulations.
